  "name": "Nagaraja COU1 — Non-cannulated pedicle screw compression-bending credibility assessment (Minimal Profile)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for FEA prediction of ASTM F1717 static compression-bending performance of a non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw construct used in posterior lumbar fixation. The FEA model ensemble (FDA, Ansys, DePuy Synthes) is compared against N=11 experimental constructs across two laboratories. All 13 V&V 40 factors assessed; one factor (Test conditions) below required level due to single test condition. Intended use is pre-market submission support for Class II spinal fixation devices under 21 CFR 888.3070. Assessment scope, patient population, and loading regime are described in the Claim and Requirement nodes referenced below.",
  "bindsRequirement": "https://uofa.net/nagaraja/req/f1717-compression-bending-noncan",
  "bindsClaim": "https://uofa.net/nagaraja/claim/fea-f1717-compression-bending-noncan",
