      "acceptanceCriteria": "Mesh convergence study must demonstrate QoI change less than 5% between successive refinements.",
      "rationale": "Three-level mesh refinement study performed on pedicle screw shank and rod junction. Von Mises stress and construct stiffness QoIs converge within 2.1% between medium and fine meshes. Required level 3 achieved."
    },
