      "acceptanceCriteria": "Residual norms and energy balance checks must be within solver tolerances.",
      "rationale": "Newton-Raphson residual norms fall below 1e-6 for all load steps. Energy balance error less than 0.3%. Iterative solver convergence confirmed across all 11 model instances."
    },
    {
