      "rationale": "Linear elastic isotropic titanium alloy (Ti-6Al-4V) constitutive model justified by strain levels remaining below 0.2% yield. Frictional contact (mu=0.2) at screw-rod interface supported by published tribology data. Required level 3 achieved."
    },
    {
