      "rationale": "N=11 constructs assembled from production-released 7.5 mm non-cannulated pedicle screws and 5.5 mm titanium rods. Lot traceability records available. Sample dimensions measured and compared to nominal CAD within 0.05 mm tolerance. Required level 3 achieved."
