      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Test conditions must replicate the range of physiologically relevant loading scenarios.",
      "rationale": "Testing performed under a single compressive offset load condition per ASTM F1717 protocol. Multi-axial or torsional loading not evaluated in this validation activity. Achieved level 2 falls below required level 3; this gap is acknowledged and accepted given the regulatory precedent for single-condition F1717 testing for Class II devices."
